</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Workflow</b> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> PRISMAGuide is now supporting multilayer workflow
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Multi layer job download via last saved jobs
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Service</b>
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Demo prints and SDS test prints at high speed when printer not licensed
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Support of new UI3 panel</b> 
</p><note type="note" id="GUID-F7739290-563C-4392-9561-2DFD61BE71A1" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> Due to the new display controller, the horizontal startup bar cannot be shown anymore. Instead, the Windows startup icon (rolling circle with dots) is shown. 
</p></note></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Controller</b>
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Job persistency on the same level as R2.5.1
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Shutdown during printing on the same level as R2.5.1
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Margin calculation on the same level as R2.5.1
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Horizontal alignment on the same level as R2.5.1
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Thumbnails on the same level as R2.5.1
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Move to top on the same level as R2.5.1
</p></li></ul></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">ADAM</b> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The information in the ADAM visit is now logged in a structural way. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Multiple languages (English, German, French, Italian, Spanish, Simplified Chinese, Japanese, Korean) can be selected. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">When at first use after installation the option is given to report the visit as an installation visit.
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Licenses</b> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> The following options are now licensed:
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Second roll in the drawer
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Matte print modes
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Print inside and double side
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">White printing
